00:13:56,639 --> 00:13:57,960
are mostly local migrant workers.

284
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,559
She often disturbs the neighbors late at night.

285
00:13:59,639 --> 00:14:01,159
If someone knocks on her door, she curses them out.

286
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,480
A street vendor said

287
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:03,679
she once went to buy cucumbers

288
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:05,759
and got into an argument over twenty cents.

289
00:14:05,759 --> 00:14:07,879
She cursed out the person's entire family.

290
00:14:08,279 --> 00:14:09,879
But I don't think anyone would kill her over that.

291
00:14:09,879 --> 00:14:11,039
No one would kill her for that, right?

292
00:14:12,679 --> 00:14:13,320
Also,

293
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,960
Did you go to all the places I told you to?

294
00:14:16,279 --> 00:14:18,000
I did, I even went to a few extra.

295
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,080
That's not what I asked.

296
00:14:19,519 --> 00:14:21,000
How did you get back?

297
00:14:21,639 --> 00:14:22,440
By bus.

298
00:14:23,759 --> 00:14:24,799
By bus?

299
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,639
What about our own car?

300
00:14:26,679 --> 00:14:27,080
No, boss.

301
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,919
Didn't you contact the repair shop?

302
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:30,120
It's in for repairs again.

303
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:33,039
Yeah.

304
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:35,519
The repair shop said it'll take several days.

305
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,759
We don't have a car to use now.

306
00:14:40,399 --> 00:14:41,320
Let's all share our thoughts.

307
00:14:41,679 --> 00:14:43,519
What do you think about this case?

308
00:14:43,519 --> 00:14:44,440
What do you mean by "let's all share"?

309
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:46,320
He pretends not to hear when he should. Did you see that?

310
00:14:46,519 --> 00:14:48,159
Why are you pretending to be clueless?

311
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,480
We're talking about serious matters.

312
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,279
Hurry up.

313
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:51,879
Speak, go on.

314
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,480
There are no signs of a struggle inside the house.

315
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:54,960
The money in the wallet hasn't been touched.

316
00:14:55,159 --> 00:14:56,080
Her financial situation

317
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,879
also makes it unlikely she was targeted for robbery.

318
00:14:58,559 --> 00:15:00,480
The initial assessment suggests it might have been done by a migrant worker.

319
00:15:00,759 --> 00:15:01,960
Has the murder weapon been found?

320
00:15:02,279 --> 00:15:03,960
We checked in front of and behind the house, and along the road.

321
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:04,960
No knife was found.

322
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:06,879
Have the victim's family members been contacted?

323
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:08,639
Brother Ma has contacted her daughter.

324
00:15:09,039 --> 00:15:11,120
She said she's on her way here from Fujian.

325
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:17,720
Don't stay silent, Wei.

326
00:15:18,639 --> 00:15:20,559
Tell us, what are your thoughts?

327
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:22,159
Captain Huang, here's what I think.

328
00:15:22,159 --> 00:15:22,799
I think

329
00:15:22,799 --> 00:15:25,679
we should intensify our investigation.

330
00:15:25,919 --> 00:15:27,519
Go through each one, one by one.

331
00:15:27,879 --> 00:15:30,360
Be sure to use the bus.

332
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:31,639
To improve efficiency,

333
00:15:31,720 --> 00:15:33,159
everyone, line up quickly, okay?

334
00:15:33,159 --> 00:15:33,960
Let's move quickly.

335
00:15:35,279 --> 00:15:37,240
Captain Huang, I'm taking the bus now.

336
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:39,879
Very good.

337
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:42,919
You're setting a great example, Wei.

338
00:15:43,399 --> 00:15:44,559
Consider this a verbal commendation.

339
00:15:48,279 --> 00:15:54,080
The late emperor passed away before he could finish his great undertaking.

340
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:55,000
Shut up.

341
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:58,519
Huang Zihong, Wang Chunyong.

342
00:15:59,039 --> 00:16:00,399
They took leave yesterday.

343
00:16:00,559 --> 00:16:01,679
They still haven't come back.

344
00:16:02,399 --> 00:16:03,200
Huang Zihong.

345
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:06,159
Go back.

346
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,600
Let me see where you think you're going.

347
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,080
Why would I run?

348
00:16:13,399 --> 00:16:14,720
You look like a cop to me.

349
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,440
What do you mean "like"? I am.

350
00:16:16,799 --> 00:16:17,519
I didn't gamble.

351
00:16:17,639 --> 00:16:19,639
If you didn't gamble, why are you running? Did I say you gambled?

352
00:16:20,399 --> 00:16:21,240
Come here and stand properly.

353
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,879
Do you know why we're looking for you?

354
00:16:26,039 --> 00:16:26,840
No, I don't.

355
00:16:26,879 --> 00:16:27,919
Where were you last night?

356
00:16:28,399 --> 00:16:29,200
Didn't do anything.

357
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:31,120
Nothing? Then why did you take leave?

358
00:16:31,759 --> 00:16:33,200
I went... I went to an internet cafe.

359
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:34,279
Which internet cafe?

360
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:36,240
Boss, Huang Zihong was at the internet cafe from ten last night

361
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:38,200
until six in the morning.

362
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,240
Yes, he stayed all night.

363
00:16:39,559 --> 00:16:40,639
Did he leave at any point?

364
00:16:40,799 --> 00:16:41,480
No.

365
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:44,080
The manager got sleepy at night and locked the door.

366
00:16:44,279 --> 00:16:45,200
If anyone wanted to leave,

367
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,279
they had to ask him to open the door.

368
00:16:46,279 --> 00:16:47,279
So no one left.

369
00:16:47,279 --> 00:16:48,679
There's no problem with Wang Chunyong either.

370
00:16:49,039 --> 00:16:50,919
I'm waiting for you at the No. 2 construction site on Lingyun Road.

371
00:16:51,279 --> 00:16:52,360
Okay, I'll be right there.

372
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:01,080
Whose is this Xue Hui?

373
00:17:01,519 --> 00:17:02,320
It's Brother Yang's.

374
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:05,000
This Xue Hui is really stubborn, Master.

375
00:17:05,680 --> 00:17:07,160
Can you not put it over by me?

376
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:10,039
One moment he says he went drinking,

377
00:17:10,039 --> 00:17:11,200
the next he says he went to see a doctor.

378
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,440
Not a single word of truth.

379
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:14,200
So what happened after that?

380
00:17:14,519 --> 00:17:16,119
He took out the handcuffs and put them down.

381
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:19,039
Where did he go?

382
00:17:19,759 --> 00:17:21,599
He rented a room by the hour with a coworker's wife.

383
00:17:22,960 --> 00:17:23,960
A coworker's wife?

384
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,960
Then where was the coworker's wife’s husband?

385
00:17:27,359 --> 00:17:29,400
He went dancing with someone at the dance hall.

386
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,039
Master, are the noodles too hot?

387
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:37,480
No, they're not too hot.

388
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:38,920
You cooked another one for me again.

389
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:48,400
Master doesn't like eating egg yolks.

390
00:17:51,119 --> 00:17:51,759
Master.

391
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:53,839
When will we ask the cafeteria

392
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:55,680
to make us some late-night snacks?

393
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,319
Even some dough drop soup would be fine.

394
00:17:57,400 --> 00:17:58,640
Is dough drop soup okay?

395
00:17:59,359 --> 00:18:00,440
When I become the director someday,

396
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:03,039
I'll open a restaurant just for you, right?

397
00:18:03,119 --> 00:18:03,960
We'll have a few hot dishes stir-fried,

398
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:04,720
and some beer.

399
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:05,960
Dough drop soup is nothing compared to that.

400
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:06,880
That sounds great.

401
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:13,759
Liu Ziming

402
00:18:13,839 --> 00:18:15,519
I'm going on a blind date tomorrow, Xiaoqing.

403
00:18:15,599 --> 00:18:16,920
Got dumped again.

404
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:18,160
Is it really over this time?

405
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,319
I really can't stand you anymore.

406
00:18:19,319 --> 00:18:20,759
I can't stand her either.

407
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:23,319
Yeah, washing so much every day, my skin's peeling.

408
00:18:23,319 --> 00:18:24,400
No one could put up with that.

409
00:18:24,799 --> 00:18:27,200
Alright, just wash if you want.

410
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,480
You smell like a corpse every day.

411
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:30,759
Covered in bloodstains, washing is good.

412
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,319
Alright, enough joking around.

413
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:35,400
After eating, take a quick nap.

414
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:36,640
You two

415
00:18:36,759 --> 00:18:38,200
Check the rest for me.

416
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:40,680
You, come with me to the construction site by the Lei River.

417
00:18:40,799 --> 00:18:43,400
Boss, that's far from the crime scene.

418
00:18:45,359 --> 00:18:46,680
You're right, it's too far.

419
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:47,519
Alright, forget it.

420
00:18:47,519 --> 00:18:48,160
Then you don't have to go.

421
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,319
Get some good rest.

422
00:18:49,319 --> 00:18:49,920
Sleep well.

423
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:50,720
Wake up naturally.

424
00:18:51,559 --> 00:18:52,559
Boss, I'll go with you.

425
00:18:52,559 --> 00:18:53,039
Alright, alright, alright.

426
00:18:53,039 --> 00:18:54,000
No need, no need, no need.

427
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:56,279
I'm not tired, I can go right now.

428
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:57,160
Now you can go again.

429
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:57,640
I can go.

430
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:58,559
Then go, go ahead.

431
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:09,559
Who are you looking for?

432
00:19:10,279 --> 00:19:11,319
I'm looking for Liu Ziming.

433
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,119
Please come with me, this way.

434
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:21,960
Ziming

435
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:23,960
Ziming

436
00:19:24,319 --> 00:19:24,720
Ziming

437
00:19:26,359 --> 00:19:26,720
Ziming

438
00:19:28,559 --> 00:19:29,400
Where's Liu Ziming?

439
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:33,200
He was just here a moment ago.

440
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:42,640
What's going on?

441
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:50,599
Why didn't you answer when I called you?

442
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,839
Aren't you going to your blind date?

443
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:54,920
Why are you looking for me?

444
00:19:56,039 --> 00:19:57,519
What if I really end up with someone else?

445
00:19:57,519 --> 00:19:58,440
As long as you're happy.

446
00:19:58,440 --> 00:20:00,759
I'm happy—happy for you.

447
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:06,839
I don't want to break up anymore.

448
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:08,519
Let's get back together.

449
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:11,400
Weren't you the one who said we weren't right for each other?

450
00:20:11,799 --> 00:20:13,200
I've thought it through.

451
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:14,799
I don't look for someone suitable.

452
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:16,319
I just look for someone I like.

453
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:17,759
I just have to make things hard for myself.

454
00:20:18,319 --> 00:20:19,519
There are so many suitable ones.

455
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:20,920
But only a few I actually like.

456
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:25,440
I just went to a crime scene this morning.

457
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:27,799
I didn't even have time to change my clothes.

458
00:20:28,200 --> 00:20:29,400
I still smell like a corpse.

459
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:30,279
Smell for yourself if you don't believe me.

460
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:33,720
Why don't you just change jobs then?

461
00:20:33,799 --> 00:20:34,839
There are so many other things you could do.

462
00:20:35,559 --> 00:20:37,720
Or go back to the wrestling team and be a coach.

463
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:39,640
You think being a coach is that easy?

464
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:41,400
No, no, no.

465
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:43,200
And being a cop is easy?

466
00:20:44,519 --> 00:20:45,480
Let me tell you,

467
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:48,400
When I joined the force, I took an oath.

468
00:20:49,359 --> 00:20:52,039
To dedicate myself to the noble cause of public security.

469
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:54,200
I will never resign in my life.

470
00:20:56,039 --> 00:20:57,160
Why not?

471
00:20:58,359 --> 00:21:01,160
There are so many cops, it wouldn't matter if you left.

472
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:05,680
Alright, alright, just hurry home.

473
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:06,559
It's dangerous to be alone.

474
00:21:06,559 --> 00:21:08,240
I'm not going back—wait,

475
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:10,000
I'm not done talking to you.

476
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:13,720
Think it over again.

477
00:21:15,319 --> 00:21:15,839
I—

478
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:16,519
Bye.

479
00:21:16,519 --> 00:21:17,160
I—

480
00:21:17,599 --> 00:21:18,279
Sir,

481
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:22,039
Please make sure she gets home safely.

482
00:21:22,039 --> 00:21:22,599
Okay.

483
00:21:22,599 --> 00:21:23,000
Alright.

484
00:21:23,319 --> 00:21:25,960
Fine, then I'll find someone else to marry tomorrow.

485
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:27,640
Alright, alright, I wish you happiness.

486
00:21:28,079 --> 00:21:28,720
Bye.

487
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:48,559
Senior Brother

488
00:21:49,839 --> 00:21:50,640
Let me do it.

489
00:21:51,559 --> 00:21:54,680
No, I can't let you delay your important work.

490
00:21:55,839 --> 00:21:57,119
Listening to success lectures again?

491
00:21:57,279 --> 00:21:58,200
What's today's topic?

492
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,240
Success, my foot.

493
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:02,440
You say that every day.

494
00:22:02,880 --> 00:22:04,720
Who knows when you'll actually succeed.

495
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:17,079
Six, five, four, three, two

496
00:22:18,559 --> 00:22:18,960
One

497
00:22:19,079 --> 00:22:19,880
Good morning, Master.

498
00:22:21,559 --> 00:22:23,720
Hey, who woke up that fool?

499
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,759
I patted him twice, but he wouldn't wake up.

500
00:22:24,759 --> 00:22:25,200
I'll go.

501
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:25,799
Alright.

502
00:22:33,359 --> 00:22:34,440
All is peaceful.

503
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:36,480
The phone rings less often.

504
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:38,599
We have fewer callouts.

505
00:22:39,519 --> 00:22:40,440
You keep talking about it.

506
00:22:40,519 --> 00:22:41,839
The more you talk about it, the more cases we get.

507
00:22:42,599 --> 00:22:43,279
Thanks.

508
00:22:47,079 --> 00:22:49,400
Master, he's awake.

509
00:22:51,599 --> 00:22:52,279
Master.

510
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:54,920
He's up, young master.

511
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:55,839
He's up, let's go.

512
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:58,279
You two go check the remaining construction sites.

513
00:22:58,279 --> 00:22:59,279
Did you hear that? Got it.

514
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:00,119
Let's go.

515
00:23:19,359 --> 00:23:20,079
This is Li.

516
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:21,039
Which Li is this?

517
00:23:21,039 --> 00:23:21,720
Li Gang.

518
00:23:22,519 --> 00:23:23,480
It's pronounced "Gang"?

519
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:27,960
Check if Li Gang is here.

520
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:29,240
Li Gang.

521
00:23:31,519 --> 00:23:32,920
Do you know where Li Gang went?

522
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:34,880
I saw him go out.

523
00:23:35,559 --> 00:23:36,400
He didn't tell me.

524
00:23:40,279 --> 00:23:41,440
He just took a half-day off.

525
00:23:42,039 --> 00:23:43,200
He still hasn't come back.

526
00:23:44,319 --> 00:23:45,920
Three people took leave today.

527
00:23:46,079 --> 00:23:47,559
Two came back, one hasn't.

528
00:23:47,559 --> 00:23:48,440
You don't know?

529
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:51,400
Don't you check attendance every day?

530
00:23:51,599 --> 00:23:53,039
You do attendance, but now he's gone.

531
00:23:53,039 --> 00:23:54,559
I can't find him either, what can I do?

532
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:56,440
Why did he take leave?

533
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,640
I don't know.

534
00:23:58,319 --> 00:23:59,000
Which room does he live in?

535
00:24:00,279 --> 00:24:01,119
Which room?

536
00:24:02,119 --> 00:24:04,240
Probably the third room in the fourth row.

537
00:24:05,319 --> 00:24:06,759
Alright, thank you.

538
00:24:12,319 --> 00:24:14,240
This is the visit report you wrote?

539
00:24:16,319 --> 00:24:18,279
Even if you wrote it with your feet, it couldn't be this bad.

540
00:24:18,279 --> 00:24:19,440
Who could even read this?

541
00:24:20,839 --> 00:24:23,240
Rewrite it for me tonight, word for word.

542
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:39,039
Who are you looking for?

543
00:24:39,599 --> 00:24:40,480
May I ask your surname?

544
00:24:40,480 --> 00:24:41,240
My surname is Zhang.

545
00:24:42,039 --> 00:24:43,039
Then it must be you.

546
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:44,640
Engineer Cao is calling for you.

547
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:47,640
We haven't finished eating yet.

548
00:24:47,640 --> 00:24:48,920
To the office, to the office.

549
00:24:51,279 --> 00:24:52,200
Let me ask you something.

550
00:24:52,559 --> 00:24:53,960
Which one is Li Gang's shop?

551
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:54,640
That one.

552
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:55,440
This one, right?

553
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:56,519
Alright, thank you.

554
00:25:16,359 --> 00:25:17,039
Master

555
00:25:18,039 --> 00:25:19,119
Cast-off bloodstain

556
00:25:19,359 --> 00:25:20,160
It really is him

557
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:22,000
What's there to get excited about?

558
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:23,920
Fights break out all the time at construction sites

